The Onboarding procedure of the product configurator includes:
* Banner
* Checklist
* Teaching tips and tour
* Assisted Setup
* Setup wizard 

<br>

After installing the app, the checklist appears on the BC homepage Banner, with a new task to complete:<br>the **Assisted Setup** of the product configurator.


<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB1_ENU.png"><br>

The Assisted Setup can be launched manually at a later time from the related list.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB2_ENU.png"><br>
<br>

The **Banner** for our apps is activated for the following Roles: BUSINESS MANAGER, BUSINESS MANAGER EVALUATION, O365 SALES other than the possible role of the user who performs the installation of the app.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB3_ENU.png"><br>
<br>

After starting the **Assisted Setup**, the welcome window appears with the possibility to:
* Access the app help
* Watch the introduction video
* Watch the extended Demo video


<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB4_ENU.png"><br>
<br>

The next step involves the possibility of launching the **New Setup Wizard** which allows to create a series of predefined data to be able to try the product configurator app. For use in a Test or Demo environment. 
Under **Learn more**, you will find the documentation page that explains in detail the data created by the New Setup Wizard. 
It is also possible to directly access the card of the items created and try the product configurator.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB5_ENU.png"><br> <br>


The next pages display in step-by-step mode all the setups necessary for the start of the product configurator. For each of the steps, the documentation page is available.
* Configurator Setup 
* Characteristics
* Rules
* Matrix Prices
* Routings and Production Boms 


<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB6_ENU.png"><br>
<br>

If enabled, **Teaching Tips** are available for the pages described above.


<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001002-0/ONB7_ENU.png"><br>